## 1. Scope & board context

This documents the estimator architecture generically, grounded in the source at the commit above. On the **`armada-ctrl-zero-h7-oem`** board the wired sensors are 3 IMUs (BMI088, ICM-20602, ICM-20948 вҖ” the last with an AK09916 magnetometer) plus a barometer and external GNSS; see `imu_clarification_2026-05-14.*` for the IMU driver/topic detail this note builds on. EKF2 only ever sees the *aggregated* uORB topics (`vehicle_imu`, `vehicle_magnetometer`, `vehicle_air_data`, `sensor_gps`, вҖҰ), never the raw `sensor_*` driver topics.

The flow studied here:

```
drivers вҶ’ sensors-module prefilter вҶ’ uORB topic вҶ’ EKF2 ingest (delay+buffer)
        вҶ’ EKF core (predict + fuse) вҶ’ output predictor вҶ’ output topics вҶ’ selector
```

